### Fluxo Operacional (Inalterado — apenas calibração interna)

```
01. Usuário → main.py         → Insere ideia + seleciona modelo
02. main.py → controller.py   → Inicializa pipeline
03. controller → planner.py   → Carrega DAG (7 tasks)
04. planner → TASK_01 (PM)    → generate_prd(ideia, contexto)
    └── PM usa PRD_TEMPLATE [ALTERADO] + PRD_EXAMPLE [ALTERADO]
    └── SectionalGenerator usa PRD_PASSES [RECALIBRADO]
    └── OllamaProvider gera com num_predict=2500 [ALTERADO]
05. planner → TASK_02 (Critic) → review_artifact(prd)
06. planner → TASK_03 (Gate)  → HUMAN_GATE ou auto-approve [--no-gate]
07. planner → TASK_04 (Arch)  → design_system(prd, approval)
08. planner → TASK_04b (Sec)  → review_security(design, prd)
09. planner → TASK_05 (Debate) → run(prd, design, security)
10. planner → TASK_06 (Plan)  → generate_plan(all_artifacts)
11. controller → relatório    → _generate_final_report [MELHORADO]
```

### Contratos de Interface (Preservados)

| Módulo | Método | Assinatura | Status |
|---|---|---|---|
| ProductManagerAgent | generate_prd | `(user_idea: str, context: str = "") -> str` | INALTERADO |
| ArchitectAgent | design_system | `(prd_content: str, approval_context: str = "") -> str` | INALTERADO |
| CriticAgent | review_artifact | `(artifact_content: str, artifact_type: str, context: str) -> str` | INALTERADO |
| SecurityReviewerAgent | review_security | `(system_design: str, prd_context: str) -> str` | INALTERADO |
| PlanGenerator | generate_plan | `(prd_system_security: str, context: str) -> str` | INALTERADO |
| DebateEngine | run | `(first_input: str, context: str, report_filename: str) -> str` | INALTERADO |
| SectionalGenerator | generate_sectional | `(artifact_type: str, user_input: str, context: str, passes: List) -> Optional[str]` | INALTERADO |
| OutputValidator | validate | `(content: str, artifact_type: str) -> Dict` | INALTERADO (retorno muda internamente) |
| OllamaProvider | generate | `(prompt: str, context: list, role: str, max_tokens: Optional[int]) -> str` | INALTERADO |

